[normal]% Yes 
[normal]Non-disabled – 46% Yes 
[normal]Q. Is there a member of staff in this prison that you can turn to for help if you have a problem? [bold]Disabled – 71
[normal]% Yes 
[normal]Non-disabled – 7
[normal]2
[normal]% Yes 
[normal]&#xa0;
