[normal]those who 
[normal]consider 
[normal]themselves 
[normal]as disabled found it significantly
[normal] 
[normal]more difficult to get a complaints form and make a complaint, than
[normal] prisoners who do not consider themselves disabled. 
[normal]The third 
[normal]question shows
[normal] 
[normal]that there is 
[normal]no significant
[normal] d
[normal]ifference
[normal] between those that consider themselve
[normal]s to have a disability and those that do not.
